Interface Storage

All Known Implementing Classes:
CampStorage, EnquiryStorage, StaffStorage, StudentStorage, SuggestionStorage
public interface Storage
Storage is an abstract class that stores objects. It contains methods to get all data, get a specific object, add items, and populate data from a CSV file.

2023-11-24
